{"id":29570,"date":"2024-01-05T17:42:07","date_gmt":"2022-01-05T12:12:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=29570"},"modified":"2023-01-30T22:00:34","modified_gmt":"2023-01-30T16:30:34","slug":"pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022 | 6 Home Office Designs With A Very Peri Twist"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Be right on trend with a home office decorated in the Pantone colour of the year 2022<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the years, the Pantone colours of the year have become an integral aspect of many industries, especially home interiors and fashion. Thus, when the Pantone Color Institute launched its brand new Pantone colour of the year 2022, none of us could keep calm. What makes this year\u2019s colour even more special is its origin and new invention. This year, Pantone, for the very first time, has come up with a brand new colour to mark the dawn of new beginnings. And so we got the PANTONE 17-3938 Very Peri \u2013 a futuristic colour palette that promises new light and aspirations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Does The Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022 Signify?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Very Peri, the Pantone colour of the year 2022, represents a colour palette that originates from the beloved colour blue and mixes with violet undertones. Thus, the colour represents serenity, stability, inspiration, wisdom and health of the Pantone blue shade. At the same time, it represents the violet undertones&#8217; creativity, playfulness and joy. Hence, Veri Peri becomes a colour that expresses the best of both shades. This new invention of<em> Pantone colour of the year 2022<\/em> gives us hope to find new opportunities and start afresh \u2013 an essential aspect of finding peaceful times in an uncertain world living with the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How To Creatively Add Very Peri To Your Home Office?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Pantone colour of the year 2022 symbolises our transformative lives \u2013 from isolation to a new kind of living with work from home and remote studying. Thus, the colour can be an essential factor in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interiors<\/a>, especially in your work corners where it can bring the much-needed positivity. So, we came up with some amazing work from home office designs with the Very Peri colour to transform your at-home work corner into a den of courageous creativity and imaginative expressions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Check out our exclusive Pantone colour of the year 2022 home office designs below.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Inspiring Modular Home Office With A Very Peri Wall Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Embrace positivity and inspiration in your home office setup with this effortless modular furnishing and a Very Peri twist. The desk is a multifunctional furniture piece that creates a compact work desk with sliding drawers. The desk evolves to form a cosy seating bench, which further forms a bookshelf. You can install this modular home office setup in any open area of your house. Complement it with a Very Peri accent wall design to create the perfect inspiring corner for your work. The Pantone colour of the year 2022 will infuse a sense of joy and artistry into your space which is sure to influence your mood when you work.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173145\/home-office-wall-design-in-pantone-color-very-peri.jpg\" alt=\"Pantone color very peri designed on a home office wall creates the perfect inspiring corner for your work\" class=\"wp-image-29573\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173145\/home-office-wall-design-in-pantone-color-very-peri.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173145\/home-office-wall-design-in-pantone-color-very-peri-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173145\/home-office-wall-design-in-pantone-color-very-peri-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173145\/home-office-wall-design-in-pantone-color-very-peri-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A gorgeous home office corner with a Very Peri accent wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Bored of your bare walls? Its time to reinvest your space!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/16114329\/bore-walls-time-to-reinvest-your-space.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022 Inspired Bedroom-Home Office<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most of us prefer having a home office setup in our bedroom rather than the living room. It can be a bit taxing to work and relax in the same room. However, we understand the challenge of space constraints in urban apartments. So, here&#8217;s a tip \u2013 go with a Veri Peri colour palette for your bedroom. This will add an elegant and soothing vibe to your sleep quarter and help you maintain a calming environment for working from the bedroom. Add a compact and functional study\/work desk unit in white. Contrast the room\u2019s Very Peri vibe with a dark <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">wood modular wardrobe<\/a> that also includes open shelves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173152\/pantone-color-of-the-year-inspired-bedroom-home-office.jpg\" alt=\"Very peri Pantone color of the year inspired home office cum bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-29574\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173152\/pantone-color-of-the-year-inspired-bedroom-home-office.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173152\/pantone-color-of-the-year-inspired-bedroom-home-office-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173152\/pantone-color-of-the-year-inspired-bedroom-home-office-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173152\/pantone-color-of-the-year-inspired-bedroom-home-office-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A calming Very Peri home office cum bedroom design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Functional Study-Work Setup With The Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have the liberty to dedicate an entire room as your home office, go for this design. This home office setup features minimal furnishings which helps to keep the rest of the space airy and clutter-free. To introduce the twist of the Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022, go with a Very Peri accent wall. Make it interesting with a subtle artistic print on the accent wall. To highlight the Very Peri theme, you can also use the colour in your furnishings. In this setup, we went for a Very Peri tinted glass front shelf cabinet in the bookshelf. You can also go for a Very Peri chair or floor rug to maintain the look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173159\/study-cum-work-room-with-pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022.jpg\" alt=\"The very peri Pantone colour of the year 2022 is ideal for study cum workroom lends a calm vibe\" class=\"wp-image-29575\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173159\/study-cum-work-room-with-pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173159\/study-cum-work-room-with-pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173159\/study-cum-work-room-with-pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173159\/study-cum-work-room-with-pantone-colour-of-the-year-2022-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A Very Peri study cum work room for home interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek Bohemian Very Peri Study\/Home Office Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/home-office-design\/\">home office design<\/a> exhibits a carefree and airy interior setup where you will enjoy working. The room has a white and Very Peri colour palette combination that creates a soothing vibe. The sleek <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-office-desk-ideas\/\">work desk design<\/a> adds to the soothing appeal. The Pantone colour of the year 2022 plays an exciting twist in the room&#8217;s interiors. Overall, this setup is ideal for a bedroom with a study\/home office unit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173139\/home-office-design-with-pantone-color-2022.jpg\" alt=\"Home office design with Pantone color 2022 very peri and white combination creates a soothing vibe\" class=\"wp-image-29572\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173139\/home-office-design-with-pantone-color-2022.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173139\/home-office-design-with-pantone-color-2022-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173139\/home-office-design-with-pantone-color-2022-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173139\/home-office-design-with-pantone-color-2022-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A sleek home office room with a Very Peri and white colour palette<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Entertainment\/Home Office With Very Peri Colour<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have an entertainment cum work desk unit as shown, you can infuse some Veri Peri colour to the wall in front of you. You could go with a Veri Peri accent wall paint colour. However, if you want to add dimension to your home office area wall, go with a digitally printed Very Peri wallpaper. You can choose an artistic wallpaper design that blends with the Very Peri appeal.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173211\/very-peri-pantone-color-wallpaper-for-home-office-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Very peri Pantone color wallpaper adds sleek appeal to your home office area wall\" class=\"wp-image-29577\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173211\/very-peri-pantone-color-wallpaper-for-home-office-wall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173211\/very-peri-pantone-color-wallpaper-for-home-office-wall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173211\/very-peri-pantone-color-wallpaper-for-home-office-wall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173211\/very-peri-pantone-color-wallpaper-for-home-office-wall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A Very Peri wallpaper design for your office setup<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to see your dream home before its built\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28145609\/want-to-see-dream-home-before-its-build.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Elegant Very Peri Home office For Two<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This home office setup is where two people can seamlessly work from home. The office design is perfect for those who are required to spend long hours at a desk. The desk has an elongated design with a cubicle layout that helps to create the perfect office environment. The home office setup also includes an artistic vibe with a Very Peri art decor. We have used the Pantone colour of the year 2022 Very Peri in interesting ways to pervade through the interiors and create a creative vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173133\/home-office-design-with-pantone-2022-color-of-the-year.jpg\" alt=\"Home office design with very peri Pantone 2022 colour of the year creates a creative vibe\" class=\"wp-image-29571\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173133\/home-office-design-with-pantone-2022-color-of-the-year.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173133\/home-office-design-with-pantone-2022-color-of-the-year-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173133\/home-office-design-with-pantone-2022-color-of-the-year-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05173133\/home-office-design-with-pantone-2022-color-of-the-year-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An elegant Very Peri home office for a couple<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How To Infuse The Magic Of The Pantone Colour Of The Year 2022 In Other Home Interiors?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several ways to integrate Very Peri into your home. Some of our ideas are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Use the Pantone colour of the year 2022 in your decorative fabrics such as drapes and blinds.<\/li><li>Add Very Peri to your furniture\u2019s upholstery such as sofa fabric and cushions.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Go for Very Peri accent walls in your living area and bedroom.<\/li><li>Give your kitchen cabinet shutters a Very Peri laminate makeover.<\/li><li>Select modern hanging lights with Very Peri tints.&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>There you go! These were some purposeful home office designs with the twist of our brand new Pantone colour of the year 2022. Like this colour, these home office setups exude a promise of creativity and energetic, joyous appeal. The colour gives us a chance to add a compassionate angle to our regular home office corners. So, dive into the magic of this gorgeous Very Peri colour and transform your home into a stylish abode.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tips-to-choose-perfect-home-painting-colors\/\">Tips To Choose Perfect Home Painting Colors<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/vastu-colours-for-home\/\">Vastu Colours For Home<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"